<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.196870>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Folsomia mofettophila sp. nov.: 1, PAO; 2, arrangement of sensilla and microsensilla on Ant. I and II; 3, maxillary outer lobe; 4, arrangement of sensilla and microsensilla on Ant. III; 5, arrangement of sensilla, microsensilla and macrochaetae on Th. II – Abd. VI; 6, chaetotaxy of dens and apical part of manubrium (anterior view); 7, chaetotaxy of manubrium, posterior side (microchaetae: ap: apical, l: lateral, lb: laterobasal, m: median, ml: mediolateral, pr: proximal; macrochaetae: L: lateral, M: median)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/196870/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

